''' Busan Kóng-vet-sṳ ''' ({{lang-ko|부산광역시/釜山廣域市}}) he sa [[Seoul]] chṳ̂-heu [[Hòn-koet]] thi-ngi thai [[sàng-sṳ]]. [[2010-ngièn]], Busan [[ngìn-khiéu]] 360 van, <ref name="busanstats1">{{cite web|url=http://english.Busan.Go.Kr/01_about/03_02.Jsp|title=Busan: Population and area of Administrative units|publisher=Dynamic Busan: Busan Metropolitan City|accessdate=2010-03-24}}</ref> Busan Tû-sṳ-khiên (pâu-koat chû-piên ke [[Gimhae Sṳ]] lâu [[Yangsan Sṳ]]) ke ngìn-khiéu yû 400 tô van. <ref name="busanpopu">http://web.Archive.Org/web/20070930211424/world-gazetteer.Com/wg.Php?X=&men=gcis&lng=en&dat=32&srt=npan&col=aohdq&pt=a&va=&srt=pnan|</ref> Busan he [[Hòn-koet]] chui-thai kóng-khiéu sàng-sṳ ya-he sṳ-kie chui fàn-mông ke hói-kóng chṳ̂-yit. <ref name="fifth">http://www.Bloomberg.Com/apps/news?Pid=newsarchive&sid=ah2Znx0vQ580 Empty Containers Clog Busan Port as Trade Slumps, bloomberg.Com – March 3, 2009 02:12 EST</ref> Busan vi-yî [[Hòn-koet]] tûng-nàm-tôn, [[Nakdong Kông]] lâu [[Suyeong Hò]] chṳ̂-kiên ke hia̍p kuk he Busan chui me̍t-si̍p ke thi-khî. Hàng-chṳn sông, fú sân he ke [[kóng-vet-sṳ]], pâu-koat 15 ke chú-yeu Hàng-chṳn-khî fò yit-ke yen. 

Busan he ke Koet-chi Fi-ngi chûng-sîm, he [[2002-ngièn Â-chû Yun-thung-fi]] lâu [[2005-ngièn]] [[APEC]] ke sṳ̀n phan sàng-sṳ, ya-he [[2002-ngièn sṳ-kie pî chiuk-khiù soi]] ke yit-ke fûn fi chhòng. 2005-ngièn 11-ngie̍t Busan siên-pu sṳ̂n phan [[2020-ngièn Ha-kui Olympic Yun-thung-fi]]. <ref>{{cite web| url = http://english.People.Com.Cn/200511/14/eng20051114_221062.Html| title = Pusan to declare bid to host 2020 Olympic Games| accessdate = December 8, 2006| author = People's Daily Online| authorlink = People's Daily| date = 2005-11-14}}</ref> chhai Hòn-koet [[Pyeongchang Khiùn]] yàng tet [[2018-ngièn Tûng-kui Olympic Yun-thung-fi]] sṳ̀n phan khièn heu, fú sân yí kói vì sṳ̂n phan 2024-ngièn fe̍t 2028-ngièn ke Ha-kui Olympic Yun-thung-fi. <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.Ytn.Co.Kr/_ln/0115_201107071651001121 |title=24 HOUR NEWS CHANNEL::::: YTN (와이티엔) |publisher=YTN |date= |accessdate=2011-09-15}}</ref>

